38:02.238 --> 38:06.242
<i>This might seem simple enough,</i>
<i>but many new cat owners get it wrong.</i>

38:06.325 --> 38:07.243
My new love.

38:08.035 --> 38:13.082
I think part of it is that they're using
the wrong items to motivate the cats.

38:15.501 --> 38:19.088
<i> Cats are more discerning</i>
